content: Our results were basically 85% to 90% based on expansion on current relationship with the current clients and 15%, 10% max comes from new logos, even though we always emphasize that it's important, the discipline of every single quarter, you add new logos to the game because this is -- we will not be relevant in terms of revenue in the short term but will be very important for -- in the year 2, year 3 for sustainable long-term growth.
